  "title": "6 Months Temp clinic assistant #HGNT",
  "description": "<p>We are hiring 6 Months Temp clinic assistant<strong> </strong>to be outsourced to our clients from reputable healthcare organizations.</p><p>Apply now!</p><p>Job Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Patient registration, or scheduling of appointments </li><li>Assisting doctors in consultation room</li><li>Dispense medication</li><li>Collecting payment</li><li>Other ad hoc duties assigned</li></ul><p>Job Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min. N/O Level </li><li>Experience in clinic assistant position</li></ul><p>All Interested candidates are invited to email your resume in MS Word format to:<br />\nhealthcare8@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>\nPlease include your full working experience, education background, notice period, expected salary.</p><p>Siow Hui Hui (Anthea)</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>Ref Code: #HGNT</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>Company Reg. No. 199601303W| EA License Number: 99C4599<br />\nWe regret to inform that only suitable candidates will be shortlisted for an\ninterview</p>",
